Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:11.87,Default,Gu,0,0,0,,{\an8}Secure defensive points and \Nprepare for a long battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:10.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ビアント）\N橋頭保を確保し
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:11.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,長期戦に備えよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:15.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１日でも戦闘を長引かせ\N帝国の首を絞め上げるぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:15.99,Default,Gu,0,0,0,,Every day that we can, we'll draw out \Nthe war and strangle the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:19.99,Default,Gu,0,0,0,,Rejoice, Major Degurechaff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:19.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ハンス）喜べ デグレチャフ少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:22.39,Sign,Gu,0,0,0,,{\an5\bord0\shad0\blur0.6\p1\fscx634\fscy25\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(642,699)}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100
